sentences.english: HEN: No. Not even if they're wildebeest.
sentences.chinese: 是的，即使是角馬他們也不會喫的。

sentences.english: The gazelles and wildebeests get along quite nicely.
sentences.chinese: 瞪羚和角馬可以完美地和諧共處。

sentences.english: There were wildebeests and he tried to save me.
sentences.chinese: 這裏有角馬他嘗試去救我。

sentences.english: A single cat finds it tricky to bring down a full-grown wildebeest.
sentences.chinese: 一隻豹子會發現自己很難撲倒一隻成年角馬。

sentences.english: The wildebeests follow, in their migration, the pattern of local rainfall.
sentences.chinese: 角馬的遷移遵循的是當地的降雨類型。
